---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<Layout
  title="Pachatopia - Where the Earth regenerates"
  description="Ecological and human regeneration project in San Carlos, Colombia: forests, soils, agroforestry, coffee, hosting and volunteering."
  lang={lang}
>
  <Header lang={lang} />
  <main>
    <Hero lang={lang} />

    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">A land coming back to life</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">San Carlos is a region of extraordinary natural beauty, deeply marked by the history of Colombia's armed conflict.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Today, both nature and local communities are rebuilding.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">At Pachatopia, we believe caring for the Earth can also help rebuild human relationships. By planting trees, regenerating soils, and nurturing biodiversity, we humbly take part in this renewal.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-12 text-center">Our actions</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">🌳 Forest regeneration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Natural reserve creation and reforestation programs to protect biodiversity and water sources.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">🌱 Agroforestry agriculture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Developing nature-inspired farming systems that produce food while regenerating soils.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">☕ Pachatopia coffee</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Coffee grown in a living ecosystem, transitioning toward regenerative agroforestry.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-3">🌍 Hosting and sharing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">A place for exchange where visitors and volunteers can discover nature and join the project.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-10">
          <a href="/en/nos-actions/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-golden-dark transition-colors">Discover our actions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-14">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-5">A living project</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia is an evolving project. Every year we plant trees, restore new plots, and develop initiatives to strengthen biodiversity and territorial resilience. Step by step, a regenerative forest ecosystem is taking shape.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-5">The Pachatopia ecosystem</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Pachatopia is designed as a place where activities support one another.</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">🌳 natural reserve · ☕ coffee and cacao plots · 🌱 tree nursery · 🏕 hosting area for visitors · 🍽 local cuisine and regional products</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">A project that aims to show we can produce, protect, and share in harmony with nature.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-5">Join the adventure</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Pachatopia is a collective adventure. Everyone can contribute to this regeneration movement.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">🌱 plant trees · ☕ discover project coffee · 🤝 volunteer · 🌍 support site development</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">Every action matters.</p>
        <a href="/en/comment-participer/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-golden-dark transition-colors">Participate in the project</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">Our conviction</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">🌱 regenerating the Earth can help regenerate human relationships<br/>🌳 planting trees is an act of hope<br/>🌍 every positive action can inspire wider change.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">☕ Why choose Pachatopia coffee?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">Our coffee is not just an agricultural product. It comes from a project that aims to regenerate land and build a more sustainable future.</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">🌱 Agriculture transitioning to agroforestry</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">🌳 A regeneration project</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3">🤝 A human project</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">🌍 A meaningful cup</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary font-semibold italic mb-6">Every cup of coffee is a seed planted for the future.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/en/le-cafe/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-golden text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-golden-dark transition-colors">☕ Discover Pachatopia coffee</a>
          <a href="/en/comment-participer/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">🌳 Sponsor a coffee tree</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-6">An invitation</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Pachatopia is open to everyone who wants to contribute to a more harmonious future. Join us and help life grow again.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang={lang} />
</Layout>
